## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

{% if values.language == 'nodejs' -%}
- Node.js 18+
- npm or yarn
{% elif values.language == 'python' -%}
- Python 3.11+
- pip
{% elif values.language == 'go' -%}
- Go 1.21+
{% endif -%}

### Installation

{% if values.language == 'nodejs' -%}
```bash
npm install
npm start
```
{% elif values.language == 'python' -%}
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```
{% elif values.language == 'go' -%}
```bash
go run main.go
```
{% endif -%}

### Health Check

